{
  "stem": "1684.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Tisch, who was a wonderful-- he was a German, but he was-- I don't believe he was even a Nazi-- but he worked-- there he was, an [NON-ENGLISH], he was the manager of Madritsch in Krakow.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So he was--he knew me, because we had some contact.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, he came into the magazine.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he said one day, there's a-- there's a-- a transport going to Brunnlitz And I said, oh can I go, can I go?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because every-- every time there was a transport, I never volunteered to go no place, because I knew it could only be worse, not-- not better.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I didn't know where I will even make it, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I always refused.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'd never officially volunteered for anything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But this, I volunteered.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because I knew that, here there is no chance to live at all, and maybe there will be a chance.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I believed in Mr.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Tisch, because he was really honest-looking to me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He had an honest face.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And so he said, OK, I can put you on the list.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I said, I have a husband and a brother-in-law.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He put them on the list, too-- who were working for Madritsch, too.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we came on the list to Schindler.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And Schindler, I never met before.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so, for the first time, when we came, of course, when the list was made, there was a lot of turmoil, and everybody wanted to be on the list.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And everybody wanted to go there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then I knew, maybe it's good.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So but then, we were only 60 or 70 people altogether, for Madritsch, taken on Schindler's List.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it the list was not touched.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "For one reason-- because they did not want to have anything done to Tisch.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
